ated weight of around 4 metric tons (4.4 short tons). |- | *''[[Yinlong]]'' | | [[Shishugou Formation]], Xinjiang, China | A small, primarily bipedal herbivore, approximately {{convert|1.2|m|ft|abbr=off|sp=us}} long, the oldest and most primitive ceratopsian known to science. |}
