{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2017}} {{Use Australian English|date=July 2017}} {{Infobox Australian political party | party_name = Stop CSG Party | party_logo = | leader = | foundation = 23 July 2013 | disbanded = 17 March 2015 | ideology = | headquarters = | holds_government = | website = | international = }} The '''Stop CSG Party''' ([[Coal Seam Gas]]) was a registered minor [[political party]] in [[Australia]] that ran candidates in the [[Australian federal election, 2013|2013 federal election]].<ref>[http://www.aec.gov.au/parties_and_representatives/party_registration/Registered_parties/stop-csg.htm Registered political parties: AEC]</ref>
